its of Painting Aluminum Garage Doors.";i:14;s:112:"Nevertheless there are also several circumstances under which it may be beneficial to repaint your garage doors.";i:15;s:67:"Adding Contrast Garage doors are a prominent feature on many homes.";i:16;s:69:"Adding a contrasting color to your home by painting your garage door.";i:17;s:144:"If your aluminum garage doors factory-painted finish has faded or has areas where the paint is completely worn its time for a new coat of paint.";i:18;s:45:"Painting aluminum doors is relatively simple.";i:19;s:94:"You will save a lot of money by painting the garage doors yourself rather than hiring someone.";i:20;s:137:"Painting aluminum is a slightly different process than painting an interior or exterior wall so use paint designed to adhere to aluminum.";i:21;s:62:"How to Paint a Metal Garage Door Five Star Painting - YouTube.";i:22;s:52:"How To Paint A Garage Door - Ace Hardware - YouTube.";i:23;s:36:"5 Best Paints for Metal Garage Door.";i:24;s:46:"5 100 2 vote s POR-15 45401 Rust Preventive C.";i:25;s:21:"Item Weight 9 pounds.";i:26;s:21:"PD10 x 10 x 9 inches.";i:27;s:21:"Item Weight 9 pounds.";i:28;s:64:"Aluminum is also used for some bi-fold closet and cabinet doors.";i:29;s:110:"Although you can paint aluminum with nearly any paint exterior-grade spray-paint leaves an even smooth finish.";i:30;s:37:"How to Paint an Aluminum Garage Door.";i:31;s:52:"Wait for a few days of good weather before starting.";i:32;s:57:"Extreme hot or cold will cause problems for paint drying.";i:33;s:58:"Like any exterior paint job it cannot be done in the rain.";i:34;s:38:"Clean the garage door before painting.";i:35;s:38:"You will want to use warm soapy water.";i:36;s:87:"While aluminum doesnt rust the manufacturer finish can be damaged with harsh chemicals.";i:37;s:118:"The best kind of paint to use on a garage door is an exterior latex paint from a paint brand that makes quality paint.";i:38;s:60:"This is true for vinyl garage doors and wooden